[normal]2.3
[normal]              
[normal]Grass roots development programmes that are delivered through the network of County Golf Partner
[normal]ships (CGPs) attracted over 86,
[normal]764 participants into golf between April 2012 
[normal]and March 2013
[normal]; 
[normal]the proportion of female participants was 44% which exceeds the current profile of all participants within golf.
